summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Antenna Site Image Sorter web app. All core functionality working correctly including landing page, upload page, category switching, component name editing, and backend APIs.
passed_tests: Landing page loads correctly with site ID input
Site ID submission navigates to upload page correctly
Upload page displays correct site ID in header
All 3 category tabs (Alpha, Beta, Gamma) switch correctly
All 13 component image placeholders are displayed
Component names are editable via Edit Component Names modal
Component name changes are saved and persist
Modal cancel functionality works correctly
Back to Home navigation works
Download ZIP button is present and functional
All backend API endpoints return correct status codes
GET /api/component-names returns 13 default names
PUT /api/component-names updates names successfully
POST /api/sites/{site_id}/upload accepts file uploads
GET /api/sites/{site_id}/category/{category} returns images
GET /api/sites/{site_id}/download provides ZIP download
Invalid category handling returns 400 error correctly
Drop zones are properly styled and interactive
Toast notifications system is working
Responsive design elements are properly implemented

success_percentage.frontend: 95% - All major UI flows working, file upload simulation limited by browser security
